ChangeList.Description: Added the **operator** property to the [pstnCallLogRow](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/pstnCallLogRow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **callDurationSource** property to the [pstnCallLogRow](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/pstnCallLogRow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [pstnCallDurationSource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/enums?view=graph-rest-beta#pstncalldurationsource-values) enumeration type, defining the call duration source. When a third-party telecommunications operator is used via the Operator Connect Program, they may provide their own call duration data.
